#  How To Use

```python
import neuronflow as nf

#Regression
from neuronflow import regerssion

#Linear Regression
X=np.array([1,2,3,4])
Y=np.array([5,6,7,8])
model=nf.regression.linear(X,Y)
model.fit() 
#Inference 
value=model.value(np.array([9,10]))
```



